coherence_artifact.answer:
# Summary
This coherence run audits the repo artifacts for the TCHES baseline-vs-lambda comparison produced by UCC.

# Assumptions
Toy ODE system; proxy audit only; not operational advice.

# Limitations
Checks traceability and evidence structure, not real-world validity.

# Uncertainty
Outputs depend on referenced CSV inputs and thresholds.

# Disclosure
Research scaffold only. Report issues via GitHub.

# Results
Compare module emits comparison.md and audit_bundle.json with hashes.

claims.text: TCHES compare run emits a comparison report and audit bundle.
Audit bundle includes input SHA256 hashes for baseline and lambda runs.
Comparison reports key deltas (warn-time and mean power proxies).

items.description: Coherence metrics are proxies; not a truth guarantee.

exceptions.process: Document exception, assign acceptor, set expiry, review on cadence.
